title: Voxel Tanks Battle Arena [Arcade, Eng, 2018]
description:
Voxel Tanks: Battle arena features classic gameplay and modern voxel graphics.
Destroy enemy tanks, using bonuses for advantages over enemies.
Three types of tanks are under the control of the player, which can be improved by picking up bonuses on the battlefields.
Thanks to the combo system of destroying opponents, the points show the maximum effectiveness of your clearing each level of the game.
Seven types of enemy tanks, three bosses, completely destructible levels and a bright retro style of graphics will keep you entertained for hours on end! 

Controls:

Player1:

WASD - Move the tank
G - Fire
 
Player2:

Arrows – Move the tank
Ctrl - Fire
